<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">س خ م:</span> <span class="c2">(السُّخْمَةُ)</span> السَّوَادُ وَ <span class="c2">(الْأَسْخَمُ)</span> الْأَسْوَدُ وَ <span class="c2">(السُّخَامُ)</span> بِالضَّمِّ سَوَادُ الْقِدْرِ. وَ <span class="c2">(سَخَّمَ)</span> اللَّهُ وَجْهَهُ <span class="c2">(تَسْخِيمًا)</span> أَيْ سَوَّدَهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>